                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-1203" type="given" value="JOHN DAVID"></interp>JOHN DAVID WADMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am clerk to Mr. Tucker, This is the book</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183602010210"></xptr>
               <p>on which I pay the prisoner for his work—I have an entry in the book, that corresponds in the mark with the piece produced—the article is not printed—the prisoner is a printer, and he has not printed it, which he should have done.</p>
               <p>
