                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined. Q.</hi> Did you give the prisoner authority to take these off the premises to pint? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, never to take them of the premises—he is finished with every thing there to do them—he was paid for this us if he had done them, but we did not know but that he had left them hanging up to dry.</p>
